# Task 3: Customer Support Chatbot

## Objective
The objective of this task is to build an AI-powered customer support chatbot that can handle common customer queries such as order status, refunds, delivery issues, and general help.

## Description
This chatbot is designed to simulate a real-world customer support assistant used by companies like Amazon, Flipkart, and Zomato. It provides instant responses, works 24/7, and improves customer experience by automating basic support tasks.

## Tools and Technologies Used
- Dialogflow (No-code chatbot builder)
- ChatGPT API
- Telegram Bot API (optional)
- Streamlit (optional)

## Features
- Greeting message for users
- Predefined answers for FAQs
- Intent recognition for user queries
- Smart fallback response when the bot does not understand
- Optional deployment on a website or Telegram

## Learning Outcomes
- Understanding how chatbots work in real-world applications
- Conversational design and intent handling
- Basics of NLP and AI-powered responses
- Deployment of chatbots on messaging platforms

## Conclusion
This project demonstrates the practical implementation of AI in customer support and showcases how automation can improve efficiency and user satisfaction.
